1951;;Bullfighter and the Lady;;American;;Budd Boetticher;;Robert Stack, Joy Page, Gilbert Roland;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bullfighter_and_the_Lady;;Chuck Regan (Robert Stack), a young American film producer travels to Mexico, where he takes up bullfighting to impress a local beauty, Anita de la Vega (Joy Page). Manolo Estrada (Gilbert Roland), an aging matador, reluctantly agrees to teach the brash, self-centered Regan.